<th>Inborn
</th>
<td>No<sup id="cite_ref-TYMO_42-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-TYMO-42">&#91;42&#93;</a></sup><sup class="reference nowrap">&#58;&#8202;<span title="Page: 13&#10;Quotation: &quot;There is a falsehood that some are born with an attraction to their own kind.... That is a malicious and destructive lie.&quot;" class="tooltip tooltip-dashed" style="border-bottom: 1px dashed;">13</span>&#8202;</sup><sup id="cite_ref-Faust_43-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Faust-43">&#91;43&#93;</a></sup><sup class="reference nowrap">&#58;&#8202;<span title="Page: 15&#10;Quotation: &quot;The false belief of inborn homosexual orientation denies to repentant souls the opportunity to change and will ultimately lead to discouragement, disappointment, and despair.&quot;" class="tooltip tooltip-dashed" style="border-bottom: 1px dashed;">15</span>&#8202;</sup><sup id="cite_ref-44" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-44">&#91;44&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-45" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-45">&#91;45&#93;</a></sup>
