<li id="cite_note-Decisions-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Decisions_25-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Decisions_25-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Decisions_25-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Decisions_25-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSchow2005" class="citation journal cs1">Schow, Ron (Fall 2005). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/sbi/articles/Dialogue_V38N03_145.pdf">"Homosexual Attractions and LDS Marriage Decisions"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i><a href="/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought">Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought</a></i>. <b>38</b> (3): 133–143. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F45227379">10.2307/45227379</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/45227379">45227379</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:254393745">254393745</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">June 18,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue%3A+A+Journal+of+Mormon+Thought&amp;rft.atitle=Homosexual+Attractions+and+LDS+Marriage+Decisions&amp;rft.ssn=fall&amp;rft.volume=38&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=133-143&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%