<li id="cite_note-Turning-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Turning_39-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Turning_39-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFRector1981" class="citation audio-visual cs1"><a href="/wiki/Hartman_Rector_Jr." title="Hartman Rector Jr.">Rector, Hartman Jr.</a> (April 1981). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K2KLpASKc2A#t=6m47s"><i>Turning the Hearts</i></a>. Salt Lake City, Utah: LDS Church.  Event occurs at 6:47. <q>[T]o be homosexual ... I am sure is an acquired addiction, just as drugs, alcohol and pornography are.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Turning+the+Hearts&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City%2C+Utah&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1981-04&amp;rft.aulast=Rector&amp;rft.aufirst=Hartman+Jr.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK2KLpASKc2A%23t%3D6m47s&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span> Video also available at <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/general-conference/1981/04/turning-the-hearts?lang=eng">churchofjesuschrist.org</a></span>
