<li id="cite_note-Faust-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Faust_43-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Faust_43-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFFaust1995" class="citation magazine cs1"><a href="/wiki/James_E._Faust" title="James E. Faust">Faust, James E.</a> (September 1995). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/ensign/1995/09/serving-the-lord-and-resisting-the-devil?lang=eng">"Serving the Lord and Resisting the Devil"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Ensign_(LDS_magazine)" title="Ensign (LDS magazine)">Ensign</a></i>. LDS Church<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 27,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Ensign&amp;rft.atitle=Serving+the+Lord+and+Resisting+the+Devil&amp;rft.date=1995-09&amp;rft.aulast=Faust&amp;rft.aufirst=James+E.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fstudy%2Fensign%2F1995%2F09%2Fserving-the-lord-and-resisting-the-devil%3Flang%3Deng&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
