<li id="cite_note-44"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-44">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation book cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.lib.byu.edu/byu/record/lee.2255698"><i>Understanding and Changing Homosexual Orientation Problems</i></a>. LDS Church. 1981. p.&#160;4. <q>Because man does have moral free agency it is inconsistent to believe that a person's homosexual orientation is inborn or locked in, and there is no real hope of change.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Understanding+and+Changing+Homosexual+Orientation+Problems&amp;rft.pages=4&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1981&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.lib.byu.edu%2Fbyu%2Frecord%2Flee.2255698&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-45"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-45">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation book cs1"><span class="id-lock-limited" title="Free access subject to limited trial, subscription normally required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.lib.byu.edu/byu/record/lee.786190?holding=ey812d1gmuud6iry"><i>Homosexuality</i></a></span>. Salt Lake City, Utah: LDS Church. 1981. p.&#160;2<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 27,</span> 2023</span>. <q>It is inconceivable that—as some involved in homosexual behavior claim—[the Lord] would permit his children to be born with desires and inclinations which would require behavior contrary to his plan.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Homosexuality&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City%2C+Utah&amp;rft.pages=2&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1981&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.lib.byu.edu%2Fbyu%2Frecord%2Flee.786190%3Fholding%3Dey812d1gmuud6iry&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span> Also quoted in <i><a href="/wiki/Newsweek" title="Newsweek">Newsweek</a></i> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.newsweek.com/masturbation-gay-leaked-mormon-church-lgtb-religion-sex-748201">here</a>.</span>
