<li id="cite_note-Welfare-53"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Welfare_53-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBrown_Jr.Bergin1973" class="citation book cs1">Brown Jr., Victor L.; <a href="/wiki/Allen_Bergin" title="Allen Bergin">Bergin, Allen E.</a> (1973). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://ia600804.us.archive.org/31/items/329384642HomosexualityWelfareServicesPacket1LDSVictorBrown/329384642-Homosexuality-Welfare-Services-Packet-1-LDS-Victor-Brown.pdf"><i>Homosexuality: Welfare Services Packet 1</i></a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. LDS Church. pp.&#160;4–5 &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>. <q>Homosexual behavior begins in various ways. Some young children are molested by strangers, acquaintances, or even relatives. ...However, not all who are molested become homosexual.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Homosexuality%3A+Welfare+Services+Packet+1&amp;rft.pages=4-5&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft.aulast=Brown+Jr.&amp;rft.aufirst=Victor+L.&amp;rft.au=Bergin%2C+Allen+E.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fia600804.us.archive.org%2F31%2Fitems%2F329384642HomosexualityWelfareServicesPacket1LDSVictorBrown%2F329384642-Homosexuality-Welfare-Services-Packet-1-LDS-Victor-Brown.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
