<li id="cite_note-56"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-56">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBergin1988" class="citation magazine cs1"><a href="/wiki/Allen_Bergin" title="Allen Bergin">Bergin, Allen</a> (October 1988). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/liahona/1988/10/questions-and-answers?lang=eng">"Questions and Answers"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Liahona_(magazine)" title="Liahona (magazine)">Liahona</a></i>. LDS Church<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 27,</span> 2023</span>. <q>For example, though a person may suffer from homosexual inclinations that are caused by some combination of biology and environment ....</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Liahona&amp;rft.atitle=Questions+and+Answers&amp;rft.date=1988-10&amp;rft.aulast=Bergin&amp;rft.aufirst=Allen&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.churchofjesuschrist.org%2Fstudy%2Fliahona%2F1988%2F10%2Fquestions-and-answers%3Flang%3Deng&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
