<li id="cite_note-Hope-66"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Hope_66-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Hope_66-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Hope_66-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKimballPetersen1970" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Spencer_W._Kimball" title="Spencer W. Kimball">Kimball, Spencer W.</a>; <a href="/wiki/Mark_E._Petersen" title="Mark E. Petersen">Petersen, Mark</a> (1970). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/HopeForTransgressors"><i>Hope for Transgressors</i></a>. LDS Church<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 27,</span> 2023</span> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Internet_Archive" title="Internet Archive">Internet Archive</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Hope+for+Transgressors&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1970&amp;rft.aulast=Kimball&amp;rft.aufirst=Spencer+W.&amp;rft.au=Petersen%2C+Mark&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2FHopeForTransgressors&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
