<li id="cite_note-Lavender-141"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Lavender_141-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWinkler2008" class="citation thesis cs1">Winkler, Douglas A. (May 2008). <span class="id-lock-limited" title="Free access subject to limited trial, subscription normally required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=7mMnAQAAIAAJ"><i>Lavender Sons of Zion: A History of Gay Men in Salt Lake City, 1950—1979</i></a></span> (PhD of Philosophy). Salt Lake City, Utah: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Utah" title="University of Utah">University of Utah</a> Department of History<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 27,</span> 2023</span> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Adissertation&amp;rft.title=Lavender+Sons+of+Zion%3A+A+History+of+Gay+Men+in+Salt+Lake+City%2C+1950%E2%80%941979&amp;rft.inst=University+of+Utah+Department+of+History&amp;rft.date=2008-05&amp;rft.aulast=Winkler&amp;rft.aufirst=Douglas+A.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D7mMnAQAAIAAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
