<li id="cite_note-194"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-194">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFRiess2016" class="citation news cs1"><a href="/wiki/Jana_Riess" title="Jana Riess">Riess, Jana</a> (November 1, 2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.sltrib.com/article.php?id=4532402&amp;itype=CMSID">"Commentary: Most U.S. Mormons approve of church's policy on gay couples, study shows"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/The_Salt_Lake_Tribune" title="The Salt Lake Tribune">The Salt Lake Tribune</a></i>. Salt Lake City, Utah<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 23,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Salt+Lake+Tribune&amp;rft.atitle=Commentary%3A+Most+U.S.+Mormons+approve+of+church%27s+policy+on+gay+couples%2C+study+shows&amp;rft.date=2016-11-01&amp;rft.aulast=Riess&amp;rft.aufirst=Jana&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.sltrib.com%2Farticle.php%3Fid%3D4532402%26itype%3DCMSID&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHomosexuality+and+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints" class="Z3988"></span></span>
