<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Homosexuality_and_the_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints&amp;action=edit&amp;section=50" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://affirmation.org/">Affirmation</a> - organization supporting LGBTQ+/SSA members and families, friends and church leaders in seeking to live fulfilling lives consistent with their values</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://northstarlds.org/">North Star</a> - community for LGBTQ+/SSA Latter-day Saints wanting to follow church teachings</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tm1cob3svWA"><i>Families Are Forever</i></a> - mini-documentary trailer about a family's push for LDS acceptance of their gay son</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.northstarsaints.org/voices-of-hope-profiles">Voices of Hope</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20141102214611/http://www.ldsvoicesofhope.org/voices.php">Archived</a> November 2, 2014, at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a> - video interviews of active church members attracted to people of the same sex</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120724193203/http://www.evergreeninternational.org/Articles.htm">Evergreen's archived collection</a> of previous church publications on homosexuality</li></ul>
